1.Sum of three numbers

Input 3 numbers Num1,Num2,Num3
Sum=Num1+Num2+Num3
Print(Sum)


2.Sum of squares of two numbers

Input 2 numbers Num1,Num2
Sum=Num1*Num1+Num2*Num2
Print(Sum)



